title: The Essential Cafe and Bistro
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Italian, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Object is to provide healthier food using organic and natural ingredients. Has a few vegetarian dishes and salads. Could make vegan dish upon request. Its open kitchen lets guests view food prep at the 25-ft oak counter. Free Wi-Fi plus a small retail selection of products. Reservation is required for dinners on Friday & Saturday.
